    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >语言说明：本游戏仅提供英文。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验一场轻松的放置冒险，每次点击都能添加色彩，进度永不停歇。解锁升级，完成任务，招募像素无人机为你绘画，在放松身心的同时观看新章节的艺术作品逐渐成形。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款增量放置点击游戏中见证数字不断攀升，游戏特色包括：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>点击上色</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/c7d6b1b386da8374d80d74eea6f8b91b.poster.avif?t=1768126014\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/c7d6b1b386da8374d80d74eea6f8b91b.webm?t=1768126014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/c7d6b1b386da8374d80d74eea6f8b91b.mp4?t=1768126014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>数字上色</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/85f0473c110928af0d20a4a033306d33.poster.avif?t=1768126014\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/85f0473c110928af0d20a4a033306d33.webm?t=1768126014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/85f0473c110928af0d20a4a033306d33.mp4?t=1768126014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自动化</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/3cd9bd77f58436b8e48e4e85d5ae6c82.poster.avif?t=1768126014\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/3cd9bd77f58436b8e48e4e85d5ae6c82.webm?t=1768126014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/3cd9bd77f58436b8e48e4e85d5ae6c82.mp4?t=1768126014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升华树</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/d91ad3b729513bdf2f708646a8f6cd12.poster.avif?t=1768126014\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/d91ad3b729513bdf2f708646a8f6cd12.webm?t=1768126014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217490/extras/d91ad3b729513bdf2f708646a8f6cd12.mp4?t=1768126014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级</strong> - 发现数百种提升进度的升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多章节</strong> - 跨越多个章节解锁全新艺术作品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>任务</strong> - 完成任务获取奖励和升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成就</strong> - 在旅程中收集数百个成就</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>离线进度</strong> - 即使离开也能享受离线进度</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轻松惬意</strong> - 放松身心，看艺术自行绘制</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Color Idle</strong>中，你的艺术冒险能走多远？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>立即加入愿望单，发售时一起开启冒险！</strong></p>",
